<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .alert-container {
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .price-highlight {
            color: #2196F3;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="alert-container">
        <h2>Price Alert Triggered</h2>
        <p>Your price alert for {{data.cryptocurrency}} has been triggered.</p>
        <p>Current Price: <span class="price-highlight">{{formatPrice data.currentPrice}}</span></p>
        <p>Target Price: {{formatPrice data.targetPrice}}</p>
        <p>Condition: Price went {{toLowerCase data.comparison}} target</p>
        <p>Triggered at: {{formatDate triggeredAt}}</p>
        <hr>
        <p><small>You received this email because you set up a price alert in your crypto portfolio.</small></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>